high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the right.
Pick up the spoon with the black handle near the edge of the counter.
Turn left and hang a left at the wall to face the white table.
Put the spoon inside the wooden bowl to the right of the tomato on the table.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon on the table.
Turn left, hang a left at end of the white table, walk around the angle of the counter and hang a left at the white stove to face the cabinets.
Open the far right cabinet, place the bowl with a spoon inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon inside a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the counter.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn to the left 90 degrees and walk across the room, turning 90 degrees to the left to face the table when you reach it.
Place the spoon in the brown cup.
Pick up the brown cup with the spoon in it.
Turn to the left 90 degrees, then again after walking to a bit and cross the room, turning another 90 degrees to the left when you reach the end, and walk towards the counter.
Put the bowl with the spoon in it into the lower cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it into a cabinet.

high_descs: turn around to the table
pick up the spoon from the table
move left to the table
drop the spoon in the plate
pick up the plate from the table
turn around and move to the cupboard
drop the plate in the cupboard
anns.task_desc: drop a plate with a spoon in it in the cupboard
